OL,3,CChild groomer arrested a month after
OL,4,Crelease to serve another 13 years
OL,6,FA taxi driver who was among the first
OL,7,Fpeople jailed following investigations
OL,8,Finto the Rotherham child grooming
OL,9,Fscandal has been locked up for another
OL,10,F13 years.
OL,12,FAdam Ali, 43, was convicted as part of
OL,13,Fthe National Crime Agency's Operation
OL,14,FStovewood, looking at historic
OL,15,Fallegations of child sexual abuse in
OL,16,Fthe town.
