OL,3,CChild groomer arrested a month after
OL,4,Crelease to serve another 13 years
OL,6,FAli, known as Razwan Razaq at the time
OL,7,Fof his offending, carried out his
OL,8,Fattacks between 2002 and 2004, using
OL,9,Fhis car to drive vulnerable young
OL,10,Fgirls to various locations where he
OL,11,Fassaulted them.
OL,13,FHe was convicted of three counts of
OL,14,Frape and three counts of sexual
OL,15,Fassault involving girls aged as young
OL,16,Fas 12 and 13 following a trial in May
OL,17,Fthis year.
