OL,3,CChild groomer arrested a month after
OL,4,Crelease to serve another 13 years
OL,6,FHis latest sentence comes little over
OL,7,Fa year after Ali was released from
OL,8,Fprison following an 11-year term for
OL,9,Fseparate sexual offences.
OL,11,FHe was arrested by the NCA just a
OL,12,Fmonth after his release after officers
OL,13,Fwere notified that he intended to
OL,14,Ftravel to Pakistan.
OL,16,FNCA senior investigator Stuart Cobb
OL,17,Fsaid: "I would once again like to pay
OL,18,Ftribute to the victims in this case,
OL,19,Fwho showed immense courage in coming
OL,20,Fforward and telling their stories.
