OL,6,F"They went through experiences no
OL,7,Fchild should ever have to."
OL,9,FOperation Stovewood is the single
OL,10,Fbiggest investigation of its kind,
OL,11,Flooking at allegations of abuse in
OL,12,FRotherham between 1997 and 2013.
OL,14,FMore than 1,100 victims have been
OL,15,Fidentified. Police have made more than
OL,16,F200 arrests and secured 34
OL,17,Fconvictions. More than 50
OL,18,Finvestigations remain ongoing.
