OL,6,FLiz Fell, Specialist Prosecutor for
OL,7,Fthe CPS, said: "Adam Ali purposefully
OL,8,Ftargeted his victims with the view
OL,9,Fthat he could exploit them for sex.
OL,11,F"Child sexual abuse is a traumatising
OL,12,Fcrime, the devastating impact of which
OL,13,Fcan last a lifetime."
